---
layout: base.njk
title: Version Info
description: Current deployment version
---

<div style="padding: 2rem;">
  <h2>Deployment Version</h2>
  <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; background: var(--surface0); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--surface1);">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      <span style="color: var(--subtext1);">Build Number:</span>
      <span style="color: var(--teal); font-weight: bold; margin-left: 0.5rem;">{{ buildInfo.buildNumber }}</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span style="color: var(--subtext1);">Deployed At:</span>
      <span style="color: var(--yellow); margin-left: 0.5rem;">{{ buildInfo.timestamp }}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
